data.description:
New on the market... Enticing ranch with a feeling of cozy comfort! Explore the versatility of this spotless ranch home that has so much to offer, 3 bedrooms, two baths, with master suite on over an acre of land with many newer updates. Updates include roof, siding, central ac, interior paint, and new flooring throughout. Outside boast a large deck and a front porch to entertain or simply relax. 2 car attached garage with plenty of space for a workshop. Take a look.. this is a great home for all your needs.

(2 separate parcels 120 X 200 front lot + .93 acre lot)
